"clone_url":"https://github.com/less/less.js.git","svn_url":"https://github.com/less/less.js","homepage":"http://lesscss.org","size":17031,"stargazers_count":17047,"watchers_count":17047,"language":"JavaScript","has_issues":true,"has_projects":false,"has_downloads":true,"has_wiki":false,"has_pages":false,"has_discussions":true,"forks_count":3397,"mirror_url":null,"archived":false,"disabled":false,"open_issues_count":244,"license":{"key":"apache-2.0","name":"Apache License 2.0","spdx_id":"Apache-2.0","url":"https://api.github.com/licenses/apache-2.0","node_id":"MDc6TGljZW5zZTI="},"allow_forking":true,"is_template":false,"web_commit_signoff_required":false,"topics":["css","language","stylesheet-language"],"visibility":"public","forks":3397,"open_issues":244,"watchers":17047,"default_branch":"master","permissions":{"admin":false,"maintain":false,"push":false,"triage":false,"pull":true}},"body":"The following is a cut down version of some library code I wrote not so long ago which worked OK in version 1.5 of less and compiles OK in less2css  V1.6.0 but not v1.7.4 (I suspect the change was made in 1.6.2 going by the changelog notes).\n\nThe problem is due to \"SyntaxError: Guards are only currently allowed on a single selector.\"\nPreviously I expected the mixin to only work on the last selector which was frequently annoying but in this rare case, quite useful.\n\nThe only way I can now think to solve this is to duplicate the of CSS so I have 2 separate rules.\n\nIs there another way or are there any plans to change the single selector guards behaviour?\n\n```\n@cta-icon: arrow-in-circle;\n@cta-icon-position: left;\n@sml-scale: 1;\n\n.cta-icon(@size: 10) when (@cta-icon = arrow-in-circle) {\n    background: url(\"cta-icon-arrow-in-circle-2.svg\") no-repeat; \n    background-size: 100% 100%; \n    width: @size; \n    height: @size; \n    position: absolute; \n    top: 0;\n}\n\n.button when (@cta-icon = arrow-in-circle) {\n    button&,\n    a& {\n        &.sml-arrow.left-arrow,\n        &.sml-arrow:not(.right-arrow) when (@cta-icon-position = left) {\n            padding-left: (@sml-scale * 2) * 10px;\n            &:before {  \n                .cta-icon(@sml-scale * 10px);\n                margin-top:  ((@sml-scale / 2) * 10px);\n                margin-left: ((@sml-scale / 2) * 10px);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/less/less.js/issues/2147/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/less/less.js/issues/2147/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"}]